title: Maldives GDP From Electricity and Water
description: GDP from Utilities in Maldives increased to 1659 MVR Million in 2021 from 1396 MVR Million in 2020. GDP from Utilities in Maldives averaged 621.66 MVR Million from 1995 until 2021, reaching an all time high of 1659 MVR Million in 2021 and a record low of 75 MVR Million in 1995. This page provides - Maldives Gdp From Utilities- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Department of National Planning, Republic of Maldives
